	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<note type="regest">Er klagt über unerträgliche <persName type="auto_name">Tyrannei</persName> des Papstes.</note>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ausus est ipsius inquisitor praeterita hyeme d. <persName type="auto_name">Ioannem Antonium</persName> a Piro, nepotem meum, <placeName ref="l55" cert="high">Bononiae</placeName> negotia sua gerentem capere captumque menses aliquot vinctum asservare eumque immeritum, utpote qui nihil dixerit aut fecerit in ea urbe contra paparum decreta.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In illis vinculis praeter durissima, quae passus est ab impurissimis illis Daemonicanis, fecit iacturam bis mille et trecentorum coronatorum:</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="regest">Näheres kann der Bruder, <persName type="auto_name">Baptista a Piro</persName>, berichten, den zu fördern <persName type="auto_name">Salis</persName> dringend bittet. Neue Nachrichten fehlen:</note>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">... praeter quae vulgo feruntur de milite a pontifice in <placeName type="auto_name">Gallias</placeName> misso.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l96" cert="high">Claven[n]ae</placeName>, die 6. iunii 1569.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
